==English==
===noun===
'''Belauan'''

#a language spoken in the Pacific; also known as '''Palauan''', for it is the language spoken in the Republic of Palau.  It is a member of the Austronesian family of languages, and is considered to be one of two languages in Micronesia belonging to the Western Austronesian group, all others considered to be members of the Oceanic subgroup.